titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: MEMBER OF SPECIALIST MULTIDISCIPLINARY TEAM INDICATOR - Description

body.p: MEMBER OF SPECIALIST MULTIDISCIPLINARY TEAM INDICATOR is the same as attribute MEMBER OF SPECIALIST MULTIDISCIPLINARY TEAM INDICATOR .

For the Cancer Outcomes and Services Data Set: Skin , MEMBER OF SPECIALIST MULTIDISCIPLINARY TEAM INDICATOR is an indication of whether the operating clinician or surgeon is a member of the specialist Multidisciplinary Team .
